Feature: Capture multi-account screenshot
  Scenario: Cached Values viewer with multiple accounts
    When I move the Dev Host to 0, 0
    And I resize the Dev Host to 1100 by 600
    And I execute command "workbench.action.closeSidebar"
    And I execute command "workbench.action.closeAuxiliaryBar"
    And I execute command "workbench.action.toggleActivityBarVisibility"
    And I execute command "kusto.seeCachedValues"
    And I wait 5 seconds
    When I evaluate "eval(atob(''))" in the webview "Cached Values"
    And I wait 2 seconds
    Then I take a screenshot "01-multi-account"
